<%= render 'signup_mailer/signup_header' %>
                          
<td style="word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto; -moz-hyphens: auto; hyphens: auto; border-collapse: collapse !important; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19px; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; padding: 0px 0px 10px;"
align="left" valign="top">
  <h3 style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 1.3; word-break: normal; font-size: 40px; margin: 0; padding: 0;" align="left">Hi,
    <%= @first %>!</h3>
  <p class="lead" style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="left">
    Welcome to EZ Sports. You have successfully signed up for the
    <%= @league %> league. Your league manager will be in touch with more information soon.
  </p>
  <p class="lead" style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="left">
    As a new member of EZ Sports, you will be contacted whenever your Coach needs to get in touch about schedules, team information, and more.
  </p>
  <p class="lead" style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="left">
    You can login anytime to see the messages your coach has sent as well as your game schedule.
  </p>
  <p class="lead" style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="left">
    The email address you will use for signing in is:
    <%= @email %>.
      <br/>
      <strong>Your temporary password is:
        <%= @password %>.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    You can change your password anytime in your profile page.
    <a href="<%=@link%>">Click here to get started.</a>
    <br/>
  </p>
  <p>
    If the link above does not work for any reason, you can visit us anytime at
    <br/>
    <%=@link%>
  </p>
  <p class="lead" style="color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="left">
    Thanks for joining EZ Sports!
  </p>
</td>

<%= render 'signup_mailer/signup_footer' %>
